    "content": "Awesome new song from a much awaited maroon 5 new album, the bass is amazing and thats\r\nI did my best to get it perfect and tab it :)\r\nif you don't understand how to play some bits, I've done a rough bass cover on youtube\r\nyou get the rythmn and stuff which is linked here:\r\n\r\nhttp://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sZJKuUbolgI&feature=youtube_gdata\r\n\r\n(Use headphones if it's too quiet :)and ignore the bobbing, i do stupid things to keep time XP )\r\n\r\nI HAVE UPDATED THE TAB NOW, THINK I PRETTY MUCH HAVE IT PERFECT, THE BASS COVER IS STILL \r\nTHERE FOR OUTLINE BUT IT'S NOWHERE NEAR PERFECT, JUST THE ROUGH RYTHMN :)\r\n\r\nSTANDARD TUNING\r\n\r\nBasically it goes like this:\r\n\r\n[tab][INTRO] X1\r\nG|------------------|\r\nD|------------------|\r\nA|-33--22--33--222--|\r\nE|------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab][VERSE 1] X2\r\nG|---5p-------4p--|\r\nD|----------------|\r\nA|-3--------2-----|\r\nE|----------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab][VERSE 2] X2\r\nG|---5p-----------4p--|\r\nD|--------------------|\r\nA|-3---------2-22-----|\r\nE|--------12\\---------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab][PRE CHORUS]\r\nG|--------------------------|\r\nD|--------------------------|\r\nA|-3-3-3~-----2-2-2----/12\\-|\r\nE|--------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab][CHORUS 1] X2\r\nG|-----------------------------------|\r\nD|------5h7-7------------3h5-5-55----|\r\nA|-7-77-------------5-55-------------|\r\nE|-----------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|--------------------------------------|\r\nD|------5h7-7------------3h5-5-7-5------|\r\nA|-7-77-------------5-55-----------7-5--|\r\nE|--------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab][CHORUS 2]  X2\r\nG|---------------9h7--------------------------|\r\nD|------5h7-77-7----9-7------3h5-5-5-7h5------|\r\nA|-7-77-----------------5-55-------------7-5--|\r\nE|--------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab][POST CHORUS] X1\r\nG|----------4p-----|\r\nD|-----------------|\r\nA|-3r-----2----2---|\r\nE|-----------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab][VERSE 1] X1\r\nG|---5p-------4p--|\r\nD|----------------|\r\nA|-3--------2-----|\r\nE|----------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab][VERSE 2] X2\r\nG|---5p-----------4p--|\r\nD|--------------------|\r\nA|-3---------2-22-----|\r\nE|--------12\\---------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab][PRE CHORUS]\r\nG|--------------------------|\r\nD|--------------------------|\r\nA|-3-3-3~-----2-2-2----/12\\-|\r\nE|--------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab][CHORUS 1] X2\r\nG|-----------------------------------|\r\nD|------5h7-7------------3h5-5-55----|\r\nA|-7-77-------------5-55-------------|\r\nE|-----------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|--------------------------------------|\r\nD|------5h7-7------------3h5-5-7-5------|\r\nA|-7-77-------------5-55-----------7-5--|\r\nE|--------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab][CHORUS 2]  X2\r\nG|---------------9h7--------------------------|\r\nD|------5h7-77-7----9-7------3h5-5-5-7h5------|\r\nA|-7-77-----------------5-55-------------7-5--|\r\nE|--------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab][BRIDGE] X1\r\nG|-----4-----2--------------------4-----2-------------4---|\r\nD|---4-----2-------4------------4-----2-------------4-----|\r\nA|-2-----0-------2------------2-----0------3-3-3--2-------|\r\nE|-------------2-----3-3-3--------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\nREST THEN\r\n\r\n[tab][CHORUS 2]  X2\r\nG|---------------9h7--------------------------|\r\nD|------5h7-77-7----9-7------3h5-5-5-7h5------|\r\nA|-7-77-----------------5-55-------------7-5--|\r\nE|--------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\nEnjoy :)\r\n\r\n************************************\r\n\r\n| p  Pull-off\r\n| \\  Slide down\r\n| /  Slide up\r\n| ~  Vibrato\r\n| h  Hammer-on\r\n| r  Release\r\n\r\n************************************",
